---
title: Lemon Ricotta Pancakes with Sausage and Orange Wedges
description: Why add ricotta cheese to pancakes? Because it makes them impossibly light and tender. Their ethereal texture and lemony bounce will send you into your day dreaming of clouds, sheep, and other fluffy-wuffy things. If anything brings you back down to earth, it’ll be the links of sausage on the side with their big, bold, and meaty juices.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/lemon-ricotta-pancakes-cacf3ca2.jpg
